---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="#TheGrind policy">
  <div
    class="bg-gray-200 p-4 rounded-lg shadow-md md:p-8 md:rounded-xl md:shadow-xl"
  >
    <p class="text-gray-800 leading-normal font-medium text-2xl">
      Privacy Policy for #thegrind
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
      This privacy policy applies to the #thegrind Android app.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-gray-800 font-medium">
      Information We Collect and How We Use It
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
      We collect information you provide directly to us, such as when you create
      a account or update your profile information. This includes your name,
      email address, and any other information you choose to provide.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
      We also collect information about your use of the app, such as your device
      type, IP address, and app usage data. This information is used to improve
      the app and provide a better user experience.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-gray-800 font-medium">Sharing of Your Information</p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
      We do not share your personal information with third parties except as
      described in this privacy policy. We may share your information with third
      party service providers who perform services on our behalf, such as
      hosting the app or analyzing usage data. These service providers are
      contractually bound to protect your personal information and may only use
      it for the specific services they are providing.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
      We may also share your information as required by law, such as in response
      to a subpoena or court order.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-gray-800 font-medium">Security</p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
      We take reasonable precautions to protect your personal information from
      unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no security measures are
      foolproof and we cannot guarantee the security of your information.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-gray-800 font-medium">Changes to This Privacy Policy</p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
      We may update this privacy policy from time to time. If we make any
      material changes, we will post the updated policy on this page and
      encourage you to review it.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-gray-800 font-medium">Contact Us</p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
      If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy practices, please
      contact us at <a href="mailto:camunoz2@gmail.com" class="text-red-500"
        >camunoz2@gmail.com</a
      >.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
